WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:01.466
Kobayashi-san?

2
00:00:01.700 --> 00:00:03.700
As an athlete sponsored by the state

3
00:00:03.766 --> 00:00:07.600
You don't just carry the expectations of your family

4
00:00:07.600 --> 00:00:09.266
Also burdened with the country

5
00:00:09.266 --> 00:00:11.266
And the expectations of the whole country for you

6
00:00:11.266 --> 00:00:12.200
What about you?

7
00:00:12.266 --> 00:00:14.800
The glory gained is not just personal

8
00:00:14.800 --> 00:00:16.200
Also national

9
00:00:16.200 --> 00:00:17.566
I hope you.

10
00:00:17.700 --> 00:00:21.166
Always maintain a love and original intention for sports

11
00:00:21.166 --> 00:00:23.066
Able to persevere

12
00:00:23.066 --> 00:00:26.266
Strive for greater glory for yourself and your country

13
00:00:26.333 --> 00:00:28.266
Setting new records all the way

14
00:00:28.500 --> 00:00:31.600
Become a new generation of legends

15
00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:38.500
Jianguo, you father and daughter are both good

16
00:00:38.700 --> 00:00:41.233
Our neighboring village is proud of you

17
00:00:41.400 --> 00:00:43.300
Jianguo I asked

18
00:00:43.600 --> 00:00:45.533
Is it the pride of our family?

19
00:00:45.533 --> 00:00:48.033
After the founding of the country

20
00:00:48.166 --> 00:00:51.433
You father and daughter are the benchmark for our whole village

21
00:00:51.800 --> 00:00:53.433
We're very proud of you.

22
00:00:54.700 --> 00:00:55.633
Xiaozhi

23
00:00:55.800 --> 00:00:59.033
I'm going to ask you to speak for everybody.

